Import:
Everything from the folder of six possible images.

State:
What is the background color
What is the current piece
current display
position

Constants:
Array of the background color options, black or white
Array of the piece options. Red, blue, or none.
Array of the filenames of the display options

Function:
A function to handle click, which sorts whether this is the first or second click.
First click: if any other Square is in selected state, remove it.
  Put this square in the selected state. Highlight adjactent possible moves.
Second click: If square is possible selected from another square, complete a move.


Effect:
Set current display, when current piece moves. Based on background color and piece.

Render:
An image from one of six options. The background color, and potentially a piece.